<template>
   <a-form
      :model="formState"
      name="basic"
      :label-col="{ span: 8 }"
      :wrapper-col="{ span: 10 }"
      autocomplete="off"
      @finish="onFinish"
      @finishFailed="onFinishFailed"
   >

   <a-form-item
      label="原域名"
      name="old_host"
      :rules="[{ required: true, message: '请输入原域名' }]"
   >
      <a-input v-model:value="formState.old_host" />
   </a-form-item>
   <a-form-item
      label="新域名"
      name="new_host"
      :rules="[{ required: true, message: '请输入新域名' }]"
   >
      <a-input v-model:value="formState.new_host" />
   </a-form-item>

   <a-form-item
      label="原OCR域名"
      name="old_ocr_host"
      :rules="[{ required: false, message: '请输入原OCR域名' }]"
   >
      <a-input v-model:value="formState.old_ocr_host" />
   </a-form-item>

   <a-form-item
      label="新OCR域名"
      name="new_ocr_host"
      :rules="[{ required: false, message: '请输入新OCR域名' }]"
   >
      <a-input v-model:value="formState.new_ocr_host" />
   </a-form-item>
   </a-form>
</template>


<script setup>
   import {onMounted, reactive} from 'vue'
   const formState = reactive({
      old_host: '',
      new_host: '',
      old_ocr_host: '',
      new_ocr_host: '',
   })
   const onFinish = () => {
      console.log('Success:', formState);
   };
   const onFinishFailed = () => {
      console.log('Failed:', formState);
   };
</script>

<style scoped>
</style>
